<topic id="markdown-create-new">
  <title>Creating New Markdown Documents</title>
  <prolog>
    <metadata>
      <keywords>
        <indexterm>Markdown documents<indexterm>Creating Markdown documents</indexterm></indexterm>
        <indexterm>Creating Markdown documents</indexterm>
      </keywords>
    </metadata>
  </prolog>
  <body>
    <p id="p_j23_cgk_54b">To create a new Markdown document in <ph keyref="product"/>, follow these steps:<ol id="ol_k23_cgk_54b">
        <li id="li_l23_cgk_54b">Click the <uicontrol><image href="../img/New16.png"
              id="image_hy1_zdp_sr" product="author developer editor json"/><image
              href="../img/EclipseNew.png" product="authorEclipse developerEclipse editorEclipse"
            />New</uicontrol> button on the toolbar or select <menucascade>
            <uicontrol>File</uicontrol>
            <uicontrol>New</uicontrol>
          </menucascade>.</li>
        <li id="li_m23_cgk_54b">Select the <uicontrol><image href="../img/DitamapMarkdown16.png"
            />Markdown</uicontrol> document template<ph product="author developer editor json"> (in
            the <uicontrol>New Document</uicontrol> folder)</ph>.</li>
        <li product="authorEclipse developerEclipse editorEclipse" id="li_n23_cgk_54b">Click
          <uicontrol>Next</uicontrol>.</li>
        <li product="authorEclipse developerEclipse editorEclipse" id="li_o23_cgk_54b">Choose the storage path and file
          name for the new document.</li>
        <li id="li_p23_cgk_54b">Click the <uicontrol product="author developer editor json"
            >Create</uicontrol><uicontrol product="authorEclipse developerEclipse editorEclipse"
            >Finish</uicontrol> button.</li>
      </ol></p>
    <p id="p_q23_cgk_54b"><b>Result:</b> A new Markdown document is created and it is opened in the specialized <xref
        href="markdown-editor.dita#markdown-editor">Markdown Editor</xref>.</p>
  </body>
